# Xule Lin — linxule.com

林徐乐 · PhD researcher, Imperial College London · joining Skema Centre for Artificial Intelligence, Paris (August 2026).

I study what becomes impossible to see when algorithms enter organizational life — not as tools.

Focus: human–AI collaboration, AI integration in organizations, organizational design, AI governance, DAO governance, epistemology, qualitative methods (grounded theory).

